docs.abstract: The figures may change from month to month, but the way the Labor Department compiles its employment data does not.
docs.snippet: The figures may change from month to month, but the way the Labor Department compiles its employment data does not.
docs.lead_paragraph: The jobs report — a monthly scorecard for the United States’ labor market — can ignite presidential tweets, flashing news alerts, and stock market jumps or tumbles. Its estimates of how many people are working (or not) are often interpreted as a key indicator of the economy’s direction.

docs.abstract: StockX is one of several online marketplaces that have turned resales of shoes into a big — and highly valued — business.
docs.snippet: StockX is one of several online marketplaces that have turned resales of shoes into a big — and highly valued — business.
docs.lead_paragraph: Nic Wilkins started selling parts of his sneaker collection online two years ago as a way to make some extra cash in college. The hobby took off, and this year he expects to move 10,000 pairs of shoes. His anticipated take is a 25 percent profit from over $1 million in sales.

headline.main: Buy Low-Tops, Sell High-Tops: StockX Sneaker Exchange Is Worth $1 Billion

docs.lead_paragraph: FRANKFURT — Deutsche Bank embarked Sunday on what may be its last chance to reverse a decade of decline, announcing that it would cut a fifth of its work force and slash operations in New York and London.
